4.2. Operational Analysis

  1. New ▸ File→New Capella Project

    Figure 3. Organisation of a Capella Project

  2. Define an Operational Capabilities diagram

    Figure 4. An OCB
    The `B`ending of the diagrams (e.g., "OCB" in the previous figure) means "Blank", meaning you can add information instead. They don’t update.
